sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as External Client
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant IstioGW as Istio Ingress Gateway
    participant LocalGW as KServe Local Gateway<br/>8445/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant KnSvc as Knative Service<br/>8012/TCP HTTP
    participant Authorino as Authorino<br/>AuthConfig
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>Go Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NGCTOKEN as NVIDIA NGC Token API<br/>authn.nvidia.com<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NGCAPI as NVIDIA NGC Catalog API<br/>api.ngc.nvidia.com<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>HTTPS/HTTP
    participant RayPod as Ray Worker Pod

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,KnSvc: Flow 1: InferenceService Serverless Deployment
        User->>Route: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
        Route->>IstioGW: TLS Passthrough
        IstioGW->>LocalGW: HTTPS/8445<br/>TLS (serving cert), mTLS (mesh)
        LocalGW->>Authorino: AuthConfig validation
        Authorino-->>LocalGW: Auth OK (anonymous or user-defined)
        LocalGW->>KnSvc: HTTP/8012<br/>plaintext (mesh-internal)
        KnSvc-->>LocalGW: Prediction Response
        LocalGW-->>IstioGW: Response
        IstioGW-->>Route: Response
        Route-->>User: JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(237, 233, 254)
        Note over Controller,NGCAPI: Flow 2: NIM Account Reconciliation
        Note right of Controller: NIM Account CR created
        Controller->>NGCTOKEN: POST /token<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: API Key (Basic Auth)
        NGCTOKEN-->>Controller: NGC Bearer Token
        Controller->>NGCAPI: GET /v2/org/models<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (NGC)
        NGCAPI-->>Controller: Model Catalog JSON
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap (model catalog)<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token (SA)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Template (ServingRuntime)<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token (SA)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create dockerconfigjson Secret<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token (SA)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Account Status<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token (SA)
    end

    rect rgb(254, 243, 199)
        Note over Controller,RayPod: Flow 3: Ray TLS Certificate Injection
        Note right of Controller: Pod created with Ray labels
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Webhook: POST /mutate--v1-pod<br/>HTTPS/9443, TLS
        Controller->>Controller: Inject init container +<br/>ray-tls-secret volume mount
        Controller-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Pod spec
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Read/Create ray-ca-tls Secret<br/>(4096-bit RSA CA, 5yr validity)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ray-tls Secret<br/>(per-pod cert keyed by IP)
        RayPod->>RayPod: Init container copies certs<br/>from Secret to emptyDir<br/>(retry: 24x10s)
        RayPod->>RayPod: Ray worker starts with mTLS
    end

    rect rgb(209, 250, 229)
        Note over Controller,ModelReg: Flow 4: Model Registry Integration
        Note right of Controller: InferenceService reconciled
        Controller->>K8sAPI: GET DataScienceCluster CR<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token (SA)
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Model Registry namespace + config
        Controller->>ModelReg: Register InferenceService metadata<br/>HTTPS or HTTP (configurable)<br/>TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token (SA)
        ModelReg-->>Controller: Registration confirmed
    end
